OL,3,CBrother fears another child will die
OL,4,Cif The Scouts continue to self-regulate
OL,6,FThe brother of a 16-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied on a Scout trip fears another
OL,8,Fchild will loose their life if the
OL,9,Forganisation continues to self-
OL,10,Fregulate.
OL,12,FBen Leonard fell to his death from the
OL,13,FGreat Orme at Llandudno during a
OL,14,FReddish Explorer Scout camping weekend
OL,15,Fin 2018.
OL,17,FAn inquest in February 2024 into the
OL,18,Fdeath of the teenager, from Stockport,
OL,19,Fruled the teenager was unlawfully
OL,20,Fkilled.
