OL,3,CBrother fears another child will die
OL,4,Cif The Scouts continue to self-regulate
OL,6,F"If nothing gets done now, another
OL,7,Fchild will die. It needs to be looked
OL,8,Fat from the inside out. It needs
OL,9,Fpulling apart and looking at under a
OL,10,Fmicroscope."
OL,12,FSharon Collins' son Scott Fanning died
OL,13,Fin 1998 on a Scout trip. She is
OL,14,Fsupporting the petition for a public
OL,15,Finquiry.
OL,17,FScott was 11 when he went on a camping
OL,18,Ftrip at Ashworth Valley. He went for a
OL,19,Fmorning walk with a group and one
OL,20,Fleader and fell 60ft down a ravine.
