OL,3,CBrother fears another child will die
OL,4,Cif The Scouts continue to self-regulate
OL,6,FCoroner David Pojur passed information
OL,7,Fabout the Scouts and one of their
OL,8,Femployees to North Wales Police who
OL,9,Fare investigating possible charges of
OL,10,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FMr Pojur also wrote a Prevention of
OL,14,FFuture Deaths Report to the Scout
OL,15,FAssociation with his concerns about
OL,16,Fhow they operate in relation to
OL,17,Fsafeguarding children in their care.
