OL,3,CBrother fears another child will die
OL,4,Cif The Scouts continue to self-regulate
OL,6,FJean Greenfield, the Leonard family's
OL,7,Flawyer said: "We need proper oversight
OL,8,Fhere. Children have died and the
OL,9,Ffindings from the inquest: they were
OL,10,Fjust extraordinary.
OL,12,F"Because they've got a Royal Charter
OL,13,Fthey are self-regulating and I just
OL,14,Fthink that has to stop."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Scouts
OL,17,FAssociation said: "Keeping young
OL,18,Fpeople safe is our top priority.
