OL,3,CBrother fears another child will die
OL,4,Cif The Scouts continue to self-regulate
OL,6,F"We look closely at all incidents to
OL,7,Fensure we are creating the safest
OL,8,Fpossible environments for the
OL,9,Fthousands of young people who take
OL,10,Fpart in Scouts every year.
OL,12,F"We are closely reviewing the
OL,13,Fcoroner's recommendations and will
OL,14,Fadopt all further changes we can to
OL,15,Fprevent such a tragic event happening
OL,16,Fagain."
